INSTALL FEATURES OF REPORTINCIDENT IN KARAF
*******************************************

features:addUrl mvn:org.apache.camel.example.reportincident/features-aries/1.0-SNAPSHOT/xml/features
features:install reportincident

Add Dynamic-Import for the commons-dbcp bundle
**********************************************
karaf@root> dev:dynamic-import 'bundleID'
Enabling dynamic imports on bundle org.apache.commons.dbcp [bundleId]


Check Web Service
*****************
http://localhost:8282/cxf/camel-example/incident?wsdl


Copy the report.txt file into the folder /temp/data/reportincident/


Control on the web site that the record has been created
********************************************************
http://localhost:8181/reportincidentweb/




